# Hackernews app

This application sample The Hackernews app that implements MVVM architecture using Koin, Room, Coroutines, Retrofit and Eventbus. <br><br>

Used <a href="https://github.com/HackerNews/API">HackerNewsAPI</a>. <br><br>



